parameters:
Customer: Can I get some Shark Chicken...? Hey, Memimi-chan,
who's that new face behind you? A newbie?

Memimi: Ah... yes, I'm... the new person starting today...
I'm learning the job by watching from behind...

Memimi: Please, not now... during a conversation... don't
move...

Memimi: I'm sorry... ah... I got my foot stepped on... by
the clumsy new person...
Memimi: Nnh, guhh--!!? Stop messing around... you...!

Memimi is being penetrated from behind while working the
cash register, as suggested by Hacker...

Memimi: (I'm definitely going to get caught...! What are
they thinking...? Do they want to ruin me?! As if the
pervert label wasn't spreading enough already... this is too
much...!)

Customer: Maybe she's feeling sick... But man, what an
erotic voice...
Memimi: Here's your Shark Chicken... kuh... uh, uh...

Customer: Hey, hurry it up! There's a line forming here!!
Memimi-chan, you're really dragging today...

Customer: Tired from your side job, maybe? Like, selling
keyholders without panties on... heh heh...
Memimi: ...! I'm so, sorry... I'll be quick... uhh...

Memimi: (The work is piling up...! Please, just behave for a
bit... I need to clear these customers quickly...)

Memimi: Gaaaahhh!!? What are you doing, you idiot?! Ahh,
hah❤️!

Hacker: (I can't hold it anymore... I'm going to finish
now!! Ughh... amazing...!)
Memimi: That's enough... stop it! Ahh, ahh❤️

Customer: What do you mean 'idiot'? Don't get cocky with the
customers... Just because you used to be some big-shot
monster, Memimi-chan...

Memimi: It's not like that... umm... I'm sorry... and please
don't talk about the past... I still have a future... I
mean, that's not what I...
Hacker: I can't take it anymore... ugh!!

Memimi: Higyuaaaaaaaahhhhh!!! Ahh, haaann❤️ Seriously, stop
it... ahh❤️, hee---!

Memimi: (He came inside meee...! Ahh, it's so hot...! This
is awful... in front of the customers... uhhhhhh...)

Customer: This is kinda scary... Is she on some weird drugs
or something...?

Customer: *whisper* Maybe she's high on too much powder...
*whisper*

Customer: Let's go... The selection here sucks anyway. Let's
head to the convenience store where the shopping district
used to be...

Memimi: Sniffle... Somehow I didn't get caught but my heart
is deeply wounded... And we lost customers too... Inside
me... sob...

Afterward, Hacker used Memimi's computer to undo the hacking
but was beaten up and ended up in the hospital...
